ABB consortium to sign Portugal dam deal . A consortium led by ASEA - Brown Boveri is to sign a contract to provide electromechanical equipment for Portugal ' s Alqueva hydroelectric dam project , the company building the dam said on Monday . State - owned EDIA said that the consortium , which includes ABB Power Generation and GEC Alsthom Neyrpic , would sign the contract , worth 8 . 7 billion escudos ( $ 50 million ) , on Wednesday . - - Lisbon editorial + ( 351 - 1 ) 3538254 
